stories.text: Many here keep personal knowledge bases, but I wonder what distribution we have for types of content collected. If you keep lists of stuff, what do you collect in your lists? Examples: Useful code snippets, places to go, books to read, startup ideas, things to teach your kids, blog post ideas, work todos, etc? If you have public lists, please, do share as well.
